Sophie Rundle https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sophie_Rundle 0 Sophie Rundle (born 21 April 1988) is an English actress best known for portraying Ada Shelby in the BBC One historical crime drama television series Peaky Blinders, as code-breaker Lucy in the ITV drama series The Bletchley Circle, and as Labia in the British/American television sitcom Episodes. She also plays Alice in Sky One's 2017 drama Jamestown.
